graph LR
    NotebookImages[Notebook Images Component]

    %% External Dependencies - Base Images
    NotebookImages -->|base image| UBI8[UBI8 Python 3.8<br/>registry.access.redhat.com]
    NotebookImages -->|base image| UBI9[UBI9 Python 3.9<br/>registry.access.redhat.com]
    NotebookImages -->|base image| C9S[CentOS Stream 9 Python 3.9<br/>quay.io/centos]

    %% External Dependencies - Libraries
    NotebookImages -->|GPU libraries| NVIDIASDK[NVIDIA CUDA 11.8 + cuDNN 8.9]
    NotebookImages -->|notebook UI| JupyterLab[JupyterLab 3.2-3.6]
    NotebookImages -->|pipeline editor| Elyra[Elyra 3.15]
    NotebookImages -->|IDE| CodeServer[code-server 4.16.1]
    NotebookImages -->|reverse proxy| NGINX[NGINX 1.22]

    %% Internal RHOAI Dependencies - Platform Components
    NotebookController[Notebook Controller] -->|spawns StatefulSets| NotebookImages
    DSPipelines[Data Science Pipelines] -->|executes runtimes| NotebookImages
    Dashboard[RHOAI Dashboard] -->|displays images| NotebookImages
    ImageStreams[OpenShift ImageStreams] -->|distributes| NotebookImages

    %% Integration Points - Notebook to Platform
    NotebookImages -.->|registers models| ModelRegistry[Model Registry]
    NotebookImages -.->|submits pipelines| DSPipelines

    %% External Services - Runtime
    NotebookImages -->|image registry| Quay[Quay.io Registry<br/>quay.io/modh/*]
    NotebookImages -->|package install| PyPI[PyPI<br/>pypi.org]
    NotebookImages -->|data storage| S3[S3 Storage<br/>AWS S3 / MinIO]
    NotebookImages -.->|database access| MongoDB[MongoDB]
    NotebookImages -.->|database access| PostgreSQL[PostgreSQL]
    NotebookImages -.->|database access| MSSQL[MS SQL Server]

    %% Kubernetes Platform
    NotebookImages -->|API server| K8sAPI[Kubernetes API]
    ImageStreams -->|pulls images| Quay
    OpenShiftRegistry[OpenShift Image Registry] -.->|optional mirror| NotebookImages

